ed="T" n="0862c16"/><persName key="A013534">釋明慧</persName>，不知何許人也。簡默恭<anchor xml:id="beg0862sgsz9"/>己<anchor xml:id="end0862sgsz9"/>，約志蠲<lb
ed="T" n="0862c17"/>明<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1978"/>，耐乎寒餒，誓求大乘。精進之鎧介躬，睡<lb
ed="T" n="0862c18"/>眠之魔退跡，是以初中後夜念誦經行<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1047"/>。時<persName key="A000294">玄<lb
ed="T" n="0862c19"/>奘<roleName>三藏</roleName></persName>在<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>北<placeName key="PL000000042745"><placeName>坊部</placeName><placeName>玉華宮</placeName></placeName>翻《大般若經》<lb
ed="T" n="0862c20"/>畢<ptr target="#n272"/>，<date key="j19636161963970" notAfter-iso="+0665-01-24" notBefore-iso="+0664-02-05"><name>麟德</name>元年</date>示滅。其夜子時，<persName key="A013534">慧</persName>旋遶佛堂，<lb
ed="T" n="0862c21"/>忽見北方有白虹四道從北亘南，橫跨<name>東<lb
ed="T" n="0862c22"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>并</sic><corr>井</corr></choice></name><ptr target="#n674"/>，直勢貫<placeName key="PL000000042410">慈恩</placeName>塔院，歷歷分明。<persName key="A013534">慧</persName>心怪焉，<lb
ed="T" n="0862c23"/>即自念曰：「昔<persName key="A002799">如來</persName>滅度，白虹十二道從西<lb
ed="T" n="0862c24"/>貫于<name>太微</name>，於是有<placeName key="PL000000048391">雙林</placeName>之滅<ptr target="#n2980"/>。今有此相，將<lb
ed="T" n="0862c25"/>非<placeName key="PL000000042745">玉華</placeName>法師有無常事邪？」申旦<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1979"/>向眾述其<lb
ed="T" n="0862c26"/>所見，眾咸怪之。至<date when-iso="+0664-03-14" key="j19636541963654">九日</date>，凶問至<placeName key="PL000000042189">京</placeName>，正符所<lb
ed="T" n="0862c27"/>見。<persName key="A013534">慧</persName>彌增篤勵，老而無懈，未知終所。</p>
